data.description: Better than new...fully fenced, landscaped and blinds throughout! This two-story layout features an open concept with plenty of space to entertain friends and family on the main level. With solid surface flooring throughout, this fashionable plan offers 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, with a study that could be transitioned to a 4th bedroom and spacious gourmet kitchen complete with an island, white cabinets, and granite countertops. Upstairs you'll find a large loft , a primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and en-suite bath, two additional bedrooms, and a bathroom including dual sinks. All appliances are included along with air conditioning, a tankless water heater and smart home package! You won't want to let this one pass you by!
